{"tid":905196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(鐵鎚扑死人)車cam影住3人持鐵鎚追死者 市民：唔夠理性","createTime":"2018-11-17T02:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T03:26:10.000Z","uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dc4acf80dc0bf4133c858756a70ea9daa5c637e9","tid":905196,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T02:56:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181117/58923875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58923875&d=QYXNQwZXmojV2I8RYOZGhwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=513e2670\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58923875&h=ac4a04fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181117/58923875</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昨晚沙田大圍一間車房的GTR被3名男子扑爆大銀幕，車房老闆與職員發現後追打其中1名涉刑毀男子，結果刑毀男被人按地毆斃。《蘋果》獲得讀者Anson提供一段當時疑為事件中死者扑玻璃後，遭車房老闆及職員追趕的片段，Anson表示，昨晚約6時，他駕車載同女友，將車停在成全路後，兩人在車廂商討食晚飯的地方，其間突然見到一名穿白衣牛仔褲的男子，由路中心走出，在其司機位旁邊走過，當時白衣男還手持木棍，他女友還問「仲乜嘢揸木棍？」，Anson估計「打架卦」，豈料隔4秒後，便見到左面行人路，一名穿深色上衣的男子急步跑往白衣男方向。<br />\n<br />\nAnson憶述當時情況指深色上衣男子後面，再有另一名男子持鐵鎚尾隨，其後還有一名穿灰色衫的男子亦跟隨在後，「三個人係一夥，好似搵梗人，向住白衣男方向急步行，我覺得好奇，但冇理由追上去，好危險。」<br />\n<br />\nAnson稍後看新聞才知發生兇殺案，回想起車cam影到的四名男子，懷疑當時首先跑過其車身邊手持木棍的是死者，而三名大漢疑是追趕死者的兇徒。「我希望將片段交畀警方，睇吓幫唔幫到忙，盡下責任。」由於他見到其中一名追趕的男子手持鐵鎚，但警方講述案情時未有透露找到鐵鎚等兇器，所以希望籍此提供一些線索予警方調查。「好似話死者太陽穴凹咗，腳踢未必凹，懷疑用鎚仔扑。」<br />\n<br />\n對於死者被人按地制服仍不斷被毆，Anson坦言有人情緒太高漲，「唔可以冷靜啲，都撳住佢，都咁傷，走得去邊，3個人仲咁大力撳住佢，攞命！我覺得其實唔使攪得咁嚴重，唔夠理性。」"},{"pid":"04f057954c6700a8a77bb2c3eeae59a3e0d03b12","tid":905196,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T02:57:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「好似話死者太陽穴凹咗，腳踢未必凹，懷疑用鎚仔扑。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0054ddb2e9b0dfe419621c865aa0f49319ccd00e","tid":905196,"uid":126436,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:00:03.000Z","msg":"只能夠講大家做野冇諗清楚 而家就負返個後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd9de2ec2c03fda2334d60abaef2d8d0d666b22","tid":905196,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:01:35.000Z","msg":"用鎚仔扑到人個頭凹左係咩罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6c901ac604f433ddefd44e52a3c395fb5632b9","tid":905196,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"一次過解決4件社會垃圾<br />\n其實都算係件好事"},{"pid":"7d5538a70a272bdc7c477002c2289bee98d1d82a","tid":905196,"uid":182933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:03:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b36ae4be74397e72dd0201399a1455d8d955d757","tid":905196,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cd9de2ec2c03fda2334d60abaef2d8d0d666b22","tid":905196,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:01:35.000Z","msg":"用鎚仔扑到人個頭凹左係咩罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"老笠"},{"pid":"03f4df2d5fc7bb5291925bbd92c0fc5204101e2c","tid":905196,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0054ddb2e9b0dfe419621c865aa0f49319ccd00e","tid":905196,"uid":126436,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:00:03.000Z","msg":"只能夠講大家做野冇諗清楚 而家就負返個後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:09:00.000Z","msg":"爆人窗個班係 打人個班都係"},{"pid":"097967cc3643638d2462d3709e49c97b29ef2079","tid":905196,"uid":26001,"like